Cloud Formation
===========================================================================================================================================================
Cloud Formation is the automation for AWS. It will allow us to create code into infrastructure

Infrastructure creation can be done
1. GUI/Console
2. CLI/Programmatic
3. Code

Cloud Formation script can be written in either 
  - JSON
  - YAML
  
Advantages 
 - Versioning
 - Reusablity
 - Testable(like Dry-run)
 
Disadvantage
 - Complex for new learner
 - Typo Errors(like space,.,;,_....)

===================================================================================================================================================================
Cloud formation will take care of the order for creating resources or provisioing
Example:
10-EC2 
2- EBS
1- EFS
2- VPC
4- Subnets

In the above scenario we have not provided the order of resources we need to create. But Cloud Formation will create VPC first and Subnet and soon in order 

===================================================================================================================================================================
 
Cloud Fromation template(CFT)
--------------------------------------------------------
Code is know as template
Template is the input and Stack(group of resources like EBS,EFS,EC2..) is the output

Delete Template , it will automatically delete the stack created by template

- By default the "automatic rollback on error" feature is enabled 
- You are charged for rolled-back infrastructure
Cloud Formation is free
